    "content": "<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><img class=\"wscnph\" src=\"//img30.360buyimg.com/venderrule//jfs/t1/258497/3/9113/293430/677c92baF61bd8a7f/3e5b44a75c48ea5e.png\" width=\"900\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【京东规则原文】</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、《京东开放平台个人/个体开店管理规则》</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=915118822988582912\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=915118822988582912</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、《京东开放平台货源平台供应商发货管理规则》</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1190896203588571136&amp;btype=1\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1190896203588571136&amp;btype=1</a> </span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、《京东开放平台运费问题纠纷处理标准》</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=3727&amp;btype=1\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=3727&amp;btype=1</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、《京东开放平台骗取他人财物细则》</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=3396\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=3396</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、《京东开放平台不当发布商品或信息细则》</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=760080125235695616&amp;btype=1\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=760080125235695616&amp;btype=1</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、《京东开放平台个人/个体合规管理规则》</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=923540006109319168&amp;btype=12\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=923540006109319168&amp;btype=12</a> </span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span st